Class DublinCoreMetadataTermsSyndicationExtension

Extends syndication specifications to provide a meta-data term resource description vocabulary.

Syntax
[Serializable]
public class DublinCoreMetadataTermsSyndicationExtension : SyndicationExtension, ISyndicationExtension, IXmlSerializable, IComparable
Remarks

The DublinCoreMetadataTermsSyndicationExtension extends syndicated content to specify all metadata terms maintained by the Dublin Core Metadata Initiative. This syndication extension conforms to the Dublin Core Metadata Initiative (DCMI) Metadata Terms 1.0 specification, which can be found at http://dublincore.org/documents/dcmi-terms/.

Context

Gets or sets the DublinCoreMetadataTermsSyndicationExtensionContext object associated with this extension.

Declaration
public DublinCoreMetadataTermsSyndicationExtensionContext Context { get; set; }
Property Value
Type Description
DublinCoreMetadataTermsSyndicationExtensionContext

A DublinCoreMetadataTermsSyndicationExtensionContext object that contains information associated with the current syndication extension.
Remarks

The Context encapsulates all of the syndication extension information that can be retrieved or written to an extended syndication entity. Its purpose is to prevent property naming collisions between the base SyndicationExtension class and any custom properties that are defined for the custom syndication extension.

Exceptions
Type Condition
System.ArgumentNullException

The value is a null reference (Nothing in Visual Basic).
